properties.value: The Supreme Rune Court is a court in RuneScape. Gnome Air is known to have filed many litigations against Ali Morrisane, specifically his magic carpet fleet, to the court.[1] According to Ali’s rug merchants, the trader is ‘not prepared to take on Gnome Air just yet.’

content:
The Supreme Rune Court is a court in RuneScape. Gnome Air is known to have filed many litigations against Ali Morrisane, specifically his magic carpet fleet, to the court.[1] According to Ali’s rug merchants, the trader is ‘not prepared to take on Gnome Air just yet.’

It is unknown if and how the court is related to the Seers' Village Courthouse.

References[edit | edit source]

  1. ^ Jagex. "Rogue Trader". 15 August 2005. (Archived from the original.) Old School RuneScape News.
rawContent:
The '''Supreme Rune Court''' is a court in [[RuneScape]]. [[Gnome Air]] is known to have filed many litigations against [[Ali Morrisane]], specifically his [[magic carpet]] fleet, to the court.{{CiteNews|newsdate=15 August 2005|url= http://services.runescape.com/m=news/rogue-trader|title=Rogue Trader}} According to Ali’s [[rug merchant]]s, the trader is ‘not prepared to take on Gnome Air just yet.’

It is unknown if and how the court is related to the [[Seers' Village Courthouse]].
